Do you know how dangerous that is? he said. the 92nd pig said, "Yes of course, I am a scientist. And I know it would help keep my home powered. Now who are you again?"

nd the wolf was like, "I'm a wolf., I am also your friend." The pig as him if his name of "Big Bad" by chance. The told him yes, and was surprised he heard of him.  We all have to eat, right?" The 92nd pig said "Sure, but there is a lot of meat at the market you could have eaten and didn't have to eat my siblings."

"Sorry about that I guess" said the wolf " but as you are a scientist, you must understand evolution and why my instincts made me do it." The 92nd pig said "Of course I do, but I also understand evolution is constantly changing every thing. Were is you mask by the way? We are in a pandemic you animal."
